{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"MLNOfflinePack","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"pack","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"withCompletionHandler:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","preciseIdentifier":"c:MLNOfflineStorage.h@T@MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The offline pack to remove.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"pack"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The completion handler to call once the pack has been","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"removed. This handler is executed asynchronously on the main queue."}]}],"name":"completion"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"As soon as this method is called on a pack, the pack becomes invalid; any","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"attempt to send it a message will result in an exception being thrown. If an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"error occurs and the pack cannot be removed, do not attempt to reuse the pack","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object. Instead, if you need continued access to the pack, suspend all packs","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and use the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/reloadPacks"},{"text":" method to obtain valid pointers to all the packs.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To detect when any call to this method results in a pack being removed, observe","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"KVO change notifications on the shared offline storage object’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" key"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"path. Removals from that array result in an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSKeyValueChangeRemoval"},{"type":"text","text":" change."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When you remove an offline pack, any resources that are required by that pack,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"but not other packs, become eligible for deletion from offline storage. Because","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the backing store used for offline storage is also used as a general purpose","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"cache for map resources, such resources may not be immediately removed if the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"implementation determines that they remain useful for general performance of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the map."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Unregisters the given offline pack and allows resources that are no longer"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"required by any remaining packs to be potentially freed.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/removePack:withCompletionHandler:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflineStorage(im)removePack:withCompletionHandler:","title":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/removepack:withcompletionhandler:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflinePack","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a region offline to a local database.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePack"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackremovalcompletionhandler","abstract":[{"text":"A block to be called once an offline pack has been completely invalidated and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"removed.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","title":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage/reloadPacks":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/reloadpacks","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/reloadPacks","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Forcibly, asynchronously reloads the "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property. At some point after this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method is called, the pointer values of the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property change, even if the underlying data for these packs has not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changed. If this method is called while a pack is actively downloading, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"behavior is undefined."}],"title":"reloadPacks","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"reloadPacks","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage/removePack:withCompletionHandler:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/removepack:withcompletionhandler:","type":"topic","title":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Unregisters the given offline pack and allows resources that are no longer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"required by any remaining packs to be potentially freed."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"title":"MLNOfflineStorage","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflineStorage"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"}}}